def: Given to sensual indulgence; gluttonous. [Obs.] Joye.
A supposed metal alleged to have been discovered in zircon.
To make a rattling noise with.You clatter still your brazen kettle. Swift.
The practice or tenets of the Ranters.
Anything lasting but a day, or a brief time; an ephemeralplant, insect, etc.

One who, or that which, revolves; specifically, a firearm (commonly a pistol) with several chambers or barrels so arranged as torevolve on an axis, and be discharged in succession by the same lock;a repeater.
On the day after the present day; on the next day; on themorrow.Summon him to-morrow to the Tower. Shak.
